fields.description: These large growing plants with beautiful flowers are great ginger plants for people who are inexperienced with growing ginger. fields.name: Costus Barbatus
fields.description: Costus barbatus is a large ginger with spiraling foliage, with striking red flower bracts and canary yellow flowers, that last all Summer long. New bracts and flowers continue to grow from the top of the inflorescence until it is a tall, red, tower of flower bracts.

fields.description:
A real leaf from an olive tree set in crystal clear eco friendly resin. Olive Tree symbolism means peace, wisdom, fertility, prosperity, immortality, and success. It is a gift from Gods linked with the renaissance and the light.

Each piece is completely made by hand. It is a process of casting individual layers of resin, adding flowers and applying a finishing layer of resin. The resin is extremely durable and has glass like properties with a high gloss finish.

fields.name: 70s Modern glass and brass terrarium

It wonderful for adding a little indoor greenery with small rooted plants or air plants. It is in excellent vintage shape with no signs of damage or wear.
